# Reproducible dev-task evidence transaction snapshots.
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/.*.backup-*/
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/.*.staging-*/

# Standard dev-task evidence-generator staging contract. `frames/` and
# `panel_frames/` are reserved transient namespaces; finalizers promote durable
# selections to `stills/` and prune the staging paths before sealing a bundle.
# Sealed media, metadata, and indexed raw scientific traces remain visible.
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/.staging/
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/frames/
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/panel_frames/
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/*.ffconcat
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/capture.stdout.txt
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/capture.stderr.txt
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/contract.stdout.txt
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/contract.stderr.txt
/docs/dev_tasks/**/assets/**/verification.stderr.txt

